<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 08:08:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>乌克兰哈尔科夫地区州长：近万人撤离</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nearly-10000-evacuated-in-ukraines-kharkiv-region-governor/articleshow/110227580.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110227580.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰东北部哈尔科夫地区州长表示，自5月10日俄罗斯军队发动地面袭击以来，已有近万人被迫离开家园。他们逃离俄罗斯士兵，俄罗斯士兵设法沿着东北边境前进 5 至 10 公里（3 至 6 英里），然后被乌克兰军队拦截。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 07:44:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nearly-10000-evacuated-in-ukraines-kharkiv-region-governor/articleshow/110227580.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国警告中国不要支持俄罗斯；北京回击与台北“军事勾结”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-warns-china-over-support-to-russia-beijing-hits-back-with-military-collusion-with-taipei/articleshow/110225463.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110225463.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着习近平和普京加强关系，美国国防官员警告中国同行，中国与俄罗斯的合作日益加强。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 06:05:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-warns-china-over-support-to-russia-beijing-hits-back-with-military-collusion-with-taipei/articleshow/110225463.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京的朋友正在帮助俄罗斯颠覆美国领导的世界秩序</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/vladimir-putins-friend-russia-ukraine-war-xi-jinping-india-and-russia-russia-and-us/articleshow/110225534.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110225534.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国一直是俄罗斯重要的外交和经济支持。 2023年，两国双边贸易额达到创纪录的2400亿美元。更重要的是，俄罗斯重视拥有一个与俄罗斯共同目标的强大盟友，即挑战美国领导的国际秩序并限制华盛顿在各自领域的影响力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 06:20:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/vladimir-putins-friend-russia-ukraine-war-xi-jinping-india-and-russia-russia-and-us/articleshow/110225534.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈萨克斯坦总统重点关注援助受洪水影响的人们</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/kazakhstan-president-focuses-on-efforts-to-aid-flood-affected-people/articleshow/110225442.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110225442.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;托卡耶夫总统主持哈萨克斯坦人民大会第28届会议，强调政府为援助洪水灾民和向新经济模式转型所做的努力。重点介绍了国际关系和哈萨克斯坦在世界护照指数中的排名。关于哈萨克斯坦洪涝灾害，托卡耶夫总统强调，哈萨克斯坦人民在洪涝灾害的困难时期表现出了团结和团结。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 06:04:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/kazakhstan-president-focuses-on-efforts-to-aid-flood-affected-people/articleshow/110225442.cms</guid></item><item><title>新加坡将于本月恢复 F-16 飞机坠毁后的飞行</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/singapore-to-resume-flying-f-16-jets-after-crash-this-month/articleshow/110225054.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110225054.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于陀螺仪错误，新加坡恢复 F-16 坠机飞行，飞行员安全弹射。飞行前应检查陀螺仪飞行控制计算机。洛克希德·马丁公司的调查正在进行中。事件发生在亚利桑那州起飞时。上一次坠机事故发生在2004年，当时美国飞行员25岁，在夜间训练期间发生事故。具体原因正在调查中。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 05:47:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/singapore-to-resume-flying-f-16-jets-after-crash-this-month/articleshow/110225054.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国驻日本大使访问中国紧张局势最前沿的南部岛屿</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-ambassador-to-japan-visits-southern-islands-at-the-forefront-of-china-tension/articleshow/110223509.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110223509.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国驻日本大使拉姆·伊曼纽尔强调威慑，并在与中国因台湾问题紧张的情况下对与那国岛和石垣岛表示支持。日本防卫态势的转变包括以远程巡航导弹的反击能力为重点的军力建设。此次访问是在南希·佩洛西访问台湾后中国向日本专属经济区发射导弹之后进行的。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 04:11:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-ambassador-to-japan-visits-southern-islands-at-the-forefront-of-china-tension/articleshow/110223509.cms</guid></item><item><title>以下是小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪如何在严格的拜登-特朗普规则下进入第一场辩论阶段</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/heres-how-robert-f-kennedy-jr-could-make-the-first-debate-stage-under-stringent-biden-trump-rules/articleshow/110224101.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110224101.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪的目标是获得参加与拜登和特朗普的辩论的资格，他面临着确保选票名额、满足投票标准、调整辩论日程以及获得副总统候选人妮可·沙纳汉的财政支持等方面的挑战。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 04:50:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/heres-how-robert-f-kennedy-jr-could-make-the-first-debate-stage-under-stringent-biden-trump-rules/articleshow/110224101.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普谎称在明尼苏达州获胜并预测 2024 年获胜</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-falsely-claims-victory-in-minnesota-and-predicts-win-in-2024/articleshow/110223860.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110223860.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普谎称在明尼苏达州 2020 年总统选举中获胜，挑战乔·拜登的胜利。他在该州面临着一场艰苦的战斗，暗示要建立新的导弹防御系统和潜在的副总统竞选搭档。特朗普对拜登发表了不敬的言论，并讨论了有关未来努力的潜在竞选策略。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 04:37:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-falsely-claims-victory-in-minnesota-and-predicts-win-in-2024/articleshow/110223860.cms</guid></item><item><title>欧盟以虚假信息为由禁止另外 4 家俄罗斯媒体在欧盟境内播出</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-bans-4-more-russian-media-outlets-from-broadcasting-in-the-bloc-citing-disinformation/articleshow/110223465.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110223465.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧盟禁止欧洲之音、俄新社、消息报和俄罗斯报在 27 国议会选举前传播有关入侵乌克兰的宣传和虚假信息。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 04:09:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-bans-4-more-russian-media-outlets-from-broadcasting-in-the-bloc-citing-disinformation/articleshow/110223465.cms</guid></item><item><title>UKMTO：红海船只被击中后受到轻微损坏</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/vessel-in-red-sea-sustains-slight-damage-after-being-struck-ukmto/articleshow/110223444.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110223444.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;红海一艘船只因胡塞武装袭击而在也门荷台达附近受损，引发地区安全担忧。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 04:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/vessel-in-red-sea-sustains-slight-damage-after-being-struck-ukmto/articleshow/110223444.cms</guid></item><item><title>即将上任的台湾总统赖智承诺稳步发展与中国的关系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/incoming-taiwan-president-lai-to-pledge-steady-approach-to-relationship-with-china/articleshow/110223437.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110223437.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;接替蔡英文的台湾新总统赖清德承诺，在北京的压力下，台海关系保持稳定。赖在就职演说中强调了台湾的全球重要性，坚持现状并主张自决。来自执政的民进党（DPP）的赖智面临着北京拒绝谈判的挑战。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 04:05:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/incoming-taiwan-president-lai-to-pledge-steady-approach-to-relationship-with-china/articleshow/110223437.cms</guid></item><item><title>泽连斯基预计俄罗斯将加强在乌克兰东北部的攻势</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/zelenskyy-expects-russian-offensive-in-northeast-ukraine-to-intensify/articleshow/110223150.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110223150.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰总统泽伦斯基强调，迫切需要加强基辅的防空防御，以应对俄罗斯在东北部推进的攻势，并寻求国际支持以增强乌克兰的防御能力。随着战争进入第三个年头，他加倍恳求盟国派遣更多防空和战斗机来对抗俄罗斯的空中优势。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 03:46:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/zelenskyy-expects-russian-offensive-in-northeast-ukraine-to-intensify/articleshow/110223150.cms</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁抗议者要求废除将跨性别者标记为精神病患者的法律</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/protesters-in-peru-demand-repeal-of-law-labeling-transgender-individuals-as-mentally-ill/articleshow/110223068.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110223068.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;秘鲁首都数百名抗议者周五举行游行，要求废除一项新法律，该法律将跨性别者等描述为患有精神疾病，以便他们能够获得健康福利。大约500名示威者和平地走在利马市中心的街道上，举着写着“不再有耻辱”和“我的身份不是疾病”的标语。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 03:46:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/protesters-in-peru-demand-repeal-of-law-labeling-transgender-individuals-as-mentally-ill/articleshow/110223068.cms</guid></item><item><title>反海地隔离墙：多米尼加总统连任王牌</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/anti-haitian-wall-dominican-presidents-reelection-trump-card/articleshow/110222524.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110222524.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一座监狱般的瞭望塔给多米尼加共和国最西南部的一片田园诗般的热带海滩蒙上了一层阴影。当多米尼加人周日在总统选举中投票时，隔离墙——现任路易斯·阿比纳德的旗舰项目——象征着他在移民问题上强硬且受欢迎的立场。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 02:57:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/anti-haitian-wall-dominican-presidents-reelection-trump-card/articleshow/110222524.cms</guid></item><item><title>泽连斯基：乌克兰拥有所需防空能力的25%</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-has-25-percent-of-needed-air-defence-zelensky/articleshow/110221133.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110221133.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周五表示，他的军队需要更多人员来鼓舞士气，这是乌克兰领导人罕见的承认。然后他们的士气就会提高，”泽连斯基告诉法新社。“这关系到他们的体力和正义。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 23:56:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-has-25-percent-of-needed-air-defence-zelensky/articleshow/110221133.cms</guid></item><item><title>副总理辞职后，尼泊尔总理寻求18个月内第四次信任投票</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/after-deputy-pm-quits-nepal-pm-to-seek-4th-confidence-vote-in-18-months/articleshow/110220180.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110220180.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尼泊尔总理普拉昌达在联盟伙伴退出后将于 5 月 20 日寻求信任投票。属于尼泊尔共产党（毛主义中心）。尼泊尔人民党撤回支持，导致辞去副总理职务。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 23:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/after-deputy-pm-quits-nepal-pm-to-seek-4th-confidence-vote-in-18-months/articleshow/110220180.cms</guid></item><item><title>北约考虑派遣训练员前往乌克兰</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nato-mulling-sending-trainers-into-ukraine/articleshow/110220092.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110220092.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于俄罗斯的进步，乌克兰出现了严重的人力短缺和战场形势恶化，包括美国在内的北约盟国正在考虑派遣军队前往乌克兰进行训练。小查尔斯·布朗将军认为，北约部署训练员是不可避免的，伊曼纽尔·马克龙等领导人以及爱沙尼亚和立陶宛等国的参与。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 23:02:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nato-mulling-sending-trainers-into-ukraine/articleshow/110220092.cms</guid></item><item><title>斯洛伐克总理再次接受手术</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/slovak-pm-undergoes-another-surgery/articleshow/110219983.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110219983.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;斯洛伐克总理罗伯特·菲科在罗斯福大学医院遭到枪击，伤势严重，接受了另一次手术。国防部长罗伯特·卡利尼亚克提到手术期间切除死亡组织</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 23:00:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/slovak-pm-undergoes-another-surgery/articleshow/110219983.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国大使称马尔代夫正在与北京讨论债务重组</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/maldives-talking-debt-restructuring-with-beijing-says-china-ambassador/articleshow/110219541.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110219541.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;国际货币基金组织警告马尔代夫债务困境风险较高，中国与马方讨论债务减免。中国大使王立新表示，债务重组可能会阻碍北京进一步提供财政援助。中方优先提供无偿援助和无偿援助，防止马尔代夫债务增加。印度在特别请求下延长了5000万美元国库券展期期限，以向马累政府表示善意。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 22:50:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/maldives-talking-debt-restructuring-with-beijing-says-china-ambassador/articleshow/110219541.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本修改法律允许离婚后共同监护</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-changes-law-to-allow-joint-custody-after-divorce/articleshow/110219374.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110219374.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;日本立法者颁布了离婚后共同监护权的立法，以解决家庭暴力、虐待儿童和非监护父母的挫败感等问题。联合国委员会建议在 2019 年为外国父母提供共同监护权。对于在日本与父母分离的未成年人，目前还没有官方统计数据。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 22:46:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-changes-law-to-allow-joint-custody-after-divorce/articleshow/110219374.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>